Package: represtools
Title: Automates basic analytic workflow
Authors@R: person("Brian", "Fannin", email = "FanninQED@eYahoo.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Version: 0.1.1
Description: This package automates creation of analysis directory structure. There are Rmd skeletons
  which encapsulate typical analytic workflow steps. Functions will create approprite modules which may
  pass data from one step to another.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
License: GPL (>=3)
SystemRequirements: GNU make
LazyData: true
Imports:
  whisker
Suggests:
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
